---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Support Us | Sahloo سهلو"
  description="Support Sahloo — help us keep all tools free and ad-free for everyone."
  canonical="https://sahloo.com/en/support/"
>
<main id="main">
  <div class="page-hero"><div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb"><a href="#" class="lang-switch">Home</a><span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span aria-current="page">Support Us</span></nav>
<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://sahloo.com/en/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Support Us"}]}</script>
    <h1 style="margin-top:14px;">❤️ Support Us</h1>
    <p>Help us keep Sahloo free for everyone.</p>
  </div></div>
  <div class="container" style="padding-bottom:64px;"><div class="support-grid">
  <div class="support-card"><div class="s-icon">☕</div><h3>Buy Us a Coffee</h3><p>A one-time donation keeps the servers running and the tools free.</p><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:14px;text-decoration:none;">Donate ❤️</a></div>
  <div class="support-card"><div class="s-icon">🔗</div><h3>Share Sahloo</h3><p>Share a tool with a friend or colleague who could benefit from it.</p></div>
  <div class="support-card"><div class="s-icon">💡</div><h3>Suggest a Tool</h3><p>Tell us what tools you need and we'll build them. Free, always.</p><a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top:14px;text-decoration:none;">Suggest →</a></div>
  <div class="support-card"><div class="s-icon">⭐</div><h3>Spread the Word</h3><p>Mention Sahloo on social media. Every mention helps us reach more people.</p></div>
</div>
<div class="prose"><h2>Why Support Sahloo?</h2>
<p>Sahloo is completely free — no sign-up, no tracking. Every tool is built for the Arabic-speaking community to make everyday calculations easier.</p>
<p>Running a website costs money (servers, domain, development time). Your support, no matter how small, helps us keep all tools free and build new ones.</p>
<h2>What We'll Never Do</h2>
<ul><li>We will never sell your data</li><li>We will never charge for basic tools</li></ul></div></div>
</main>
</Layout>
